And blaſted Kenrick's bays;
                        A little, hypocritical, lying, cowardly raſcal, to pick a man's pocket of a thouſand pound, before he himſelf had fingered a farthing of the money! See the particulars of his raſcality, on this occaſion, in the preface to the fourth edition of my Duelliſt.
                           KENRICK. Vivá vocé.
